        <abstract> 
<p>Glad CW has written on phyllotaxy [<hi rend="italic">Mem. Am. Acad. Arts &amp; Sci.</hi> n.s. 9 (1867–73): 379–415].</p>  
<p>Sure that CW’s pamphlet [<hi rend="italic">Darwinism</hi> (1871)] will do cause good service.</p> 
            <p>Grateful for kindness to sons in America.</p>
